{"tid":661905,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內地客崇光爆買堵路　警方驅趕","createTime":"2018-05-12T03:31:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-12T05:17:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"69c8e901e3f4395f0591dab59e8ba32579d34d77","tid":661905,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T03:31:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180512/20388302\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180512%2F20388302&d=3juTG67kHkovhAVMyh4CYsKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=1e830a11\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180512%2F20388302&h=69d6d7fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180512/20388302</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月12日 <br />\n<br />\n內地客崇光爆買堵路　警方驅趕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180512/large/12la7p03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180512%2Flarge%2F12la7p03.jpg&h=fb132594&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警方昨日驅散阻塞銅鑼灣行人路的內地客。易仰民攝 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】銅鑼灣東角道一帶昨日陷入一片渾沌，因百貨公司大減價活動，引來大批內地客掃貨。顧客搜刮戰利品後，在百貨公司門外拆貨入篋，導致東角道及駱克道一帶行人路癱瘓，需要藍帽子出動驅散集結人群。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180512/large/12la7p20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180512%2Flarge%2F12la7p20.jpg&h=5b6a0af1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■不少內地客在行人路上擺放戰利品，佔領行人路。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180512/large/12la7p05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180512%2Flarge%2F12la7p05.jpg&h=3d7c2c13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■大批內地客昨日為大減價活動來港，逼爆崇光各樓層。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行人路攤篋擺放戰利品<br />\n<br />\n年度消費大事崇光感謝周年慶，割價傾銷大量名牌護膚品及日用品。昨晨清早已有人排隊等候崇光開門搶先入貨，排隊人龍一度擠滿正門外的軒尼詩道和東角道交界，人群甚至溢出馬路。<br />\n<br />\n現場所見，大舉掃貨者以內地客為主，他們逼爆崇光各樓層之餘，掃貨完畢後，大軍還重重包圍崇光外的大街小巷，其中東角道和駱克道交界最擠擁，人群至下午仍未消散。他們在行人路上攤開大篋小篋以便擺放戰利品；行人路完全被他們佔領，一名失明人士欲經現場進入地鐵站也受阻。<br />\n<br />\n經歷多個小時的混亂，警方終於出動，一批藍帽子到場驅散阻塞通道的內地客。不過他們撤離東角道一邊行人路後，又轉移陣地到對面行人路。<br />\n<br />\n內地客丁先生與幾位女士專程為大減價活動來港，租住銅鑼灣的酒店，昨日清晨4時便開始排隊，花了逾12萬元狂掃化妝品，聲稱自用。一心想買護膚品給母親的港人黃小姐則抱怨，內地人繼搶奶粉、演唱會票、炒樓之後，連平價貨也來搶，覺得困擾。<br />\n<br />\n■記者林社炳  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n2019公眾假分散　多長周末　 新春請2連放9日<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n翠湖經理收賄囚半年"},{"pid":"fa00f1ce4caa6deeab110d463d06053d27304a4c","tid":661905,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T03:32:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e0acc32ca529d6763486b90e06b2f86dfb67c936","tid":661905,"uid":23833,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T03:58:19.000Z","msg":"垃撚垃"},{"pid":"2517ff19f59c16e6ddcadf09359420e9caabb14b","tid":661905,"uid":77196,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T03:59:58.000Z","msg":"點解警察唔放催淚彈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16808ba6fef6d5d0f4f369b84a81f9ac914346d3","tid":661905,"uid":28366,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T04:00:11.000Z","msg":"光復銅鑼灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34d6d3be0e56cdc23271beece2a7ccfc8b3a52f3","tid":661905,"uid":177590,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T04:01:50.000Z","msg":"低賤"},{"pid":"c64b8082f251316e87f680a49261f3e7bd069cfa","tid":661905,"uid":11001,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T04:02:33.000Z","msg":"佔領老銅，正式啟動 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea792a58dcb0152210d079f0710dacb445b0c17","tid":661905,"uid":2394,"